Class BanknoteDispenserMR

java.lang.Object
com.unitedbankingservices.AbstractDevice<BanknoteDispenserObserver>
com.unitedbankingservices.banknote.AbstractBanknoteDispenser
com.unitedbankingservices.banknote.BanknoteDispenserMR
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBanknoteDispenser, IDevice<BanknoteDispenserObserver>
public final class BanknoteDispenserMR extends AbstractBanknoteDispenser
Represents a device that stores banknotes (as known as banknotes, paper money, etc.) of a particular denomination to dispense them as change. This device cannot receive additional banknotes automatically, but must be manually reloaded.
